1. *Dovde* smo stigli pešice. (*Here*) - We've walked *here* so far.
2. Idući *dovde* nisam video nikoga poznatog. (*Towards here*) - While walking *towards here* I didn't see anyone familiar.
3. *Dovde* smo se vozili, a sada ćemo peške. (*Until here*) - We've been riding *until here*, and now we'll walk.
4. Oni su *dovde* došli ranije. (*Here*) - They arrived *here* earlier.
5. *Dovde* sam te razumeo, ali dalje ne. (*Until here*) - I understood you *until here*, but not further.
6. Hoćemo li *dovde* da idemo zajedno ili svako svojim putem? (*Up to here*) - Are we going to go together *up to here*, or will we go our separate ways?
7. *Dovde* si me razočarao, ali nadam se da ćeš se iskupiti. (*So far*) - *So far* you've disappointed me, but I hope you'll make it up.
8. *Dovde* mi se dopada, ali mislim da bi bilo još bolje tamo. (*Here*) - I like it *here*, but I think it would be even better over there.

Note: The word "dovde" can be translated in various ways depending on the context.